    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="x08290009" svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>ESC SWITCHED 5 VOLT SENSOR SUPPLY</title>
        <para>The ESC provides a 5 volt sensor signal for several sensors on the vehicle. A DTC will be logged if the 5
            volt signal is shorted to ground. A short in any sensor using the signal or on any circuit carrying the
            signal will cause all sensors to be inoperative.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
